BIGBANG will comeback in February ahead of their Coachella performance.

EXO is scheduled to comeback in early 2026.

Kpop idols that will enlist or discharge from the military soon:

NCT's Doyoung and Jungwoo have announced their enlistment date, December 8th.

SEVENTEEN's Mingyu is expected to enlist in the military soon, along with DK.

All BTS members have now finished they military service, and they are working on their comeback now.

NCT's Taeyong will be discharged on December 14th.

Both EXO's Kai and Sehun were discharged, and are working on the group's comeback.
